    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the expressionistic style inspired by children's art characteristic of a group formed in 1948 by artists from Copenhagen, Brussels, and Amsterdam. The formalized group is often referred to as a movement, though technically it is a corporate body made up of founding members, rather than a generalized movement with unaffiliated members.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
